WIDGET REST API

A rest api to manage widgets

Built with:
	Java 8, Spring Boot

Run the application with default port(8080):
	> mvn spring-boot:run 

Run with a different port:
	> mvn spring-boot:run  -Dspring-boot.run.arguments=--server.port=8088
	
Run the application in H2 mode by changing "h2.enabled" property to "true"
	> mvn spring-boot:run -Dspring-boot.run.arguments=--h2.enabled=true

Run all integration and unit tests:
	> mvn test
	
Documentation of the api can be found as a swagger file which is published under "/swagger.yml" path.

To visualize documentation copy the content of swagger.yml in swagger editor(https://editor.swagger.io/)
